Advantages of Confluence:
1. Content management
2. Search
3. Confluence Templates
4. Integration with JIRA
5. Page and File versioning
6. Feedback
7. User Management
8. Add-ons and plugins


1. Content Management:
    a. Content management includes the creation, maintenance, organization, and deletion of content.
    b. The content creation tools are easy to use and include a variety of functions- from basic text formatting, creating tables all the way to linking documents and embedding macros.
    c. The content can be organized into separate spaces, sorted and arranged in hierarchical order as required.
